# Public portfolio allowlist.
# The original workspace is preserved locally, but only curated/public files are
# tracked by default to avoid committing personal documents, credentials, raw
# notebooks, executables, or large generated artifacts by accident.

*

!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!.env.example
!README.md
!requirements.txt

!src/
!src/**

!docs/
!docs/**

!notebooks/
!notebooks/**

!assets/
!assets/**

!data/
!data/README.md
!data/sample/
!data/sample/**

# Keep full historical daily charts local unless a cleaned sample is prepared.
financial/
financial/*.csv

# Local/private configuration and runtime artifacts stay ignored even if added
# under public folders later.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.exe
*.dll
*.lnk
*.bat
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.h5
*.ckpt
*.index
*.data-00000-of-00001
checkpoint
